        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收升359點 滙控騰訊成動力  電池及光伏股飆",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後升幅擴大，恒指收升359點，滙控(00005)升逾2%，龍頭股成升市動力，電池及光伏股飛升，生科醫藥及機器人股也造好，恒指及國指一周累升逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日收報25417點，升359點或1.43%，今早競價時段開報25136，升77點或0.31%，最低報25090，升32點或0.13%，為全日低位，午後突破上午高位，最高報25471，升413點或1.65%，為全日高位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_FI_source-web_01530-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_FI_source-web_01530-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_FI_source-web_01530-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日升108點或1.95%，報5687點，今早開報5602，升23點或0.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日升120點或1.34%，報9057點，今早開報8960，升22點或0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計恒指累升340點或1.36%，科指累計升13點或0.23%，國指累升1.23%或110點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指報25398點，升425點或1.7% ，低水20點 ; 科指期貨報5698點，升121點或2.17%，高水11 點; 國指期貨報9046點，升134點或1.5%，低水11點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交2999.45億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍頭股成升市動力，滙控(00005)升2.51%報102.1元 ; 騰訊(00700)升2.19%，報605.5元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)升1.54%，報131.8元，三股合共推升恒指132點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電池股飛升，贛鋒鋰業(01772)揚12.55%，報34.98元; 天齊鋰業(09696)升13.33%，報44.56元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏相關股份全日領升，協鑫科技(03800)以全日高位收市，報1.47元，彈12.2% ; 協鑫新能源(00451)飆26.67%，報1.14元 ; 信義光能(00968)升7.54%，報3.71元，為表現最佳藍籌股；同系的信義玻璃(00868)升4.65%，報8.55元；信義能源(03868)飛升10.32%，報1.39元; 福萊特玻璃(06865)抽高9.03%，報12.2元 ; 新特能源(01799)飆17.28%，報8.89元。國家工信部、市場監督管理總局稱依法治理光伏等產品低價競爭、引導地方有序佈局光伏、鋰電池產業。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒隆地產(00101)升6.13%，報8.49元，升幅藍籌股中居第三位。希慎(00014)升1.65%，報15.4元 ; 新鴻基地產(00016)升0.82%，報92.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生科股及醫藥股普遍造好，三生製藥(01530)升18.24%，報35.66元，成交入20大 ; 中國生物製藥(01177)升6.2%，報8.83元，升幅藍籌股中居第二位 ; 翰森製藥(03692)升4.56%，報37.1% ; 石藥(01093)升3.32%，報11.19元 ; 藥明生物(02269)升4.71%，報36.94元 ; 藥明康德(02359)升4.22%，報113.6元 ; 藥明合聯(02268)升3.56%，報65.44元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_FI_source-web_01530-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250520_FI_source-web_01530-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三生製藥2024年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">機器人股炒上，地平線機器人(09660)全日飆9.12%，報9.81元，成交入20大 ; 優必選(09880)升4.39%，報107元。  </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股受捧，中芯(00981)升4.82%，報58.7元 ; 華虹半導體(01347)升4.16%，報47.58元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新東方(09901)跌1.52%，報37.66元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n</div>",
