        },
        {
            "title": "港股升逾400點回順   信義光能升逾7%藍籌中表現最佳",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股節節向上，恒指最高報25471，升413點或1.65%，現報25451，升393點或1.57%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指升129點或2.31%，報5707點 ; 國指升9077點︳升140點或1.58%，報9077點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交2130.97億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信義光能(00968)升7.25%，報3.7元; 中芯(00981)升6.52%報59.65元 ; 紫金礦業(02899)升6.15%，報28.32元，為表現最佳三藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新東方(09901)跌1.41%，報37.7元 ; 京東健康(06618)跌1.09%，報37.7元。為表最差兩藍籌股。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15233676-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be400%e9%bb%9e%e5%9b%9e%e9%a0%86-%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a9%e5%85%89%e8%83%bd%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be7%e8%97%8d%e7%b1%8c%e4%b8%ad%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e6%9c%80%e4%bd%b3",
